## **Step 4: Plot Graph in WEKA**

1. After running classifiers
2. Right-click on result in **Result list**
3. Click **Visualize classifier errors**
4. Scatter plot of correct vs incorrect predictions is shown

(You can also take screenshot for lab record)

---

## **Conclusion (Write This Exactly)**

> Decision Tree and Rule-Based classification were implemented using WEKA on a categorical dataset.
> The Decision Tree algorithm achieved higher accuracy compared to the Rule-Based classifier.
> Hence, Decision Tree is more efficient for categorical data prediction.


